race.description: Local Trainers Cadgee Park Racing Mdn Plate
race.comment: BROADWAY DANCER (9) resumes after six months and was fourth at Oakbank before the break. Trialled well and looks set for a bold return. HASTA LA WIZARD (14) led for much of the way at Penola before fading. Winkers are off again and blinkers go on. Keep safe. FRENCH LOVE (10) should find this easier than the last attempt and has claims off the placing at Gunbower prior. LOVE STREET (11) gets blinkers on and could be a big improver at start number two.
